body:
I'm bored, so I'm starting a discussion. What was your first skin? Doesn't matter if it was gifted or bought. If you want, put a little history behind it :)
Mine was Battlecast {{champion:161}} 

I started playing when Vel'Koz was released, and contemplated buying him for about a week or so (was feeling nervous about it because he looked complicated and I think I was level 13 or something), then I just yolo'd it and spent the first amount of rp I bought on him. A second week later I got his skin because I loved playing him so much. Still play him to this day :D
